long_desc.thetext: The current style of the stplit button is not very good. In fact the whole spit button is a set of two buttons with each of them having his own theming. The focus looks wired because only the left button is focused and so on.
Created attachment 476 Design Mockup made by Christoph Bloemer.
to Martin - you raised your hand ;-)

To Martin's and my understanding the existing theming is correct. It's by intention that a split button consists of those two separate buttons: one for an immediate action, the other for a drop down (history for instance). The proposed solution is identical to a selectbox, therefore wouldn't work. Closed as invalid.
